Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.84,0:00:08.66,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本片輕描淡寫地講述了南家三姐妹平凡的日常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.89,0:00:10.95,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要過度期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.66,0:00:00.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.15,0:00:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  一起吃便當吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  今天沒帶來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.35,0:00:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去買嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.76,0:00:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早點去比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思你們先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.92,0:00:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  想喝點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.01,0:00:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶茶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.82,0:00:30.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼幫我帶個牛奶咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶茶和牛奶咖啡對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.56,0:00:33.17,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.18,0:00:34.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.22,0:00:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛的速水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪  你想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.63,0:00:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用問
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.47,0:00:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要把我親手做的便當交給南春香
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.42,0:00:49.15,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.61,0:00:50.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以很痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.44,0:00:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還用問
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是把我親手做的便當給南春香吃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:00:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把便當還我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲啊  保阪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.50,0:01:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然忘了享受料理的真正目的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.39,0:01:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.23,0:01:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開便當可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再回想一次  你真正想傳達給春香的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.48,0:01:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正想傳達的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.92,0:01:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多汗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.32,0:01:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快些擦乾的話會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.20,0:01:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必著急這汗還有的流呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.59,0:01:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.79,0:01:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在社團活動結束後讓南春香替我拭去汗水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  那就需要把春香拉進我們女子排球部
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧  保阪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:51.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要的是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.92,0:01:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先謝謝了  速水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.48,0:02:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南春香  不來打排球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  保阪學長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.71,0:02:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香去買麵包了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光吃麵包會營養失調的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南春香不可能不知道這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  今天只是偶爾忘了做飯而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南春香在作為學生的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是撫養兩個女兒的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣食和學業並存並不是那麼容易的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是女兒而是妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此  我能支援她就是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.12,0:02:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的料理  我的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.07,0:02:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.65,0:02:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不是脫衣服的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我  南春香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上為你製作最棒的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.67,0:02:49.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說話啊…
