Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪學長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.60,0:04:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也不參加社團活動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得為家人準備飯菜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.19,0:04:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就沒有辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有幾人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家中有幾人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:56.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:04:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:04:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:11.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你經常不去社團露面是因為要給家人準備飯菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我考慮了下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:19.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓你能專心於社團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來為你的家人準備飯菜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上今天已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以便當的形式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在梅雨的季節
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食物中毒必須嚴防
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.19,0:05:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也沒有疏忽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這便當特別加入了大量的醋和生薑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要介意  作為排球部部長我只是做了理所應當的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  接去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保阪學長  我不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  說理由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果接受了這個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會招來某些人的不好的誤解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:05:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好的誤解是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.66,0:06:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不能說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:04.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我不去追問你的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想讓家人吃上熱騰騰的飯菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.77,0:06:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去後想好好地做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱騰騰的飯菜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一家人其樂融融地吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是名為家人的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來剛才你說了「啊  對了」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是忽然想起了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有想起來什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:36.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  不繼續深入家庭的話題了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但隨時都可以來找我幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人給做飯的話的確是很輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才在想什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹的那個眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想讓成熟的女性給做飯的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  成熟的料理的做法？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問的是「如何讓自己變成熟」和「如何做出好吃的料理」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨意混在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我沒有在問夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道怎麼成熟地去做料理哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  裸體圍裙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:38.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是天才嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對變態嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我充斥著無所不能的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說仁美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然間提高料理的水平很困難
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.91,0:07:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有誰作為特定的對像的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如去問問這個人的喜好？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜好？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡甜的或是辣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.78,0:08:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就從這裏開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過對方的喜好清楚地知道了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.07,0:08:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都可以來找我幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若無其事地詢問喜好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜還是辣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.43,0:08:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:39.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹的那個眼神是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決心自己做料理的堅定地眼神！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔！怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡超甜的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為你們女子排球部做的特製便當
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了淳子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺噁心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我做的還好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.55,0:09:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個雨什麼時候才能停啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.21,0:09:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  已經第幾天了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田已經是第幾次問這句話了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  第幾次了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田  你討厭下雨嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是討厭下雨…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不盡情享受現在的梅雨季節會很吃虧的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎樣去享受？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:09:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是濺到水了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.68,0:10:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:06.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.16,0:10:11.83,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說內田啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  不要玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來追我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.66,0:10:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.63,0:10:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濕了一身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.93,0:10:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也向我道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身濕透了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪冬馬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪內田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你們兩個才對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過最後千秋也加入了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了大家都去泡澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.09,0:10:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.69,0:10:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田糾結於下雨的問題才會變得這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.08,0:10:58.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪冬馬把水濺在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家互相玩水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後千秋都用傘玩高爾夫了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濺都濺濕了也都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  春香你剛才說了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近一直下雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.25,0:11:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗衣服都不幹的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋的衣服不夠給她們換的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  所以要把我的衣服拿出來給她們穿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒絕！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我明天就沒有衣服穿了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天其它的衣服不就干了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是哪裏來的保證啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香你的借她們不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的衣服尺寸上很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定也不會奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  不是什麼大事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋的「不是什麼大事」多數時候都是大事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:11:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得浴巾都拿去洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.64,0:12:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干的一條都沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…用什麼擦身子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.61,0:12:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底只要把校服弄幹不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會這麼快干的  再說也沒有內衣換了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那春香的借她們不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尺寸會不合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.91,0:12:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴巾應該也還沒干
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她們要用什麼來擦身子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.72,0:12:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒有麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼在浴巾的替代品到來之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡情享受泡澡吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:42.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別玩了這裏很窄的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.80,0:12:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢淋我  看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒潑到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:53.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有小毛巾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要洗的東西又增加了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:13:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就會幹了  再等一等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道會這樣就做些其他的衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  內田來玩摔跤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要享受當下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在衣服干之前就安安靜靜地等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋大人  請您務必讓雨雲打道回府
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也差不多開始想念藍天了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋的話一定能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明天還要和藤岡踢足球的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.52,0:13:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別祈禱  也別拜我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐  你也說說她們讓她們冷靜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你千秋  這樣下去明天就沒有衣服換了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐  連你也這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
